{"tid":497650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關心香港政治嘅同我入撚晒嚟","createTime":"2017-12-13T04:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T05:01:25.000Z","uid":336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f583b92181d1ff61f3863410b9d7d4c85b6ceb52","tid":497650,"uid":336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:01:30.000Z","msg":"今晚就開始正式審議事規則。<br />\n希望大家真係關心吓，唔好停留係笑鳩泛民同本土。<br />\n泛民嘅照出席泛民搞嘅合法集會。<br />\n如果你係本土嘅話，覺得好撚憎泛民，覺得琴晚陳國強俾人請離場屌係離撚譜的話，唔緊要，咁希望你地可以召集同主持一個合法集會，係以本土意識形態為主，大家各有各做。<br />\n呢件事唔係睇互相仆街咁簡單，而係殺到埋身唇寒齒亡，係時候要放下黨派之爭。<br />\n有人先有力量，有力量先有籌碼，先可以談判。<br />\n希望大家可以加入，無論咩位置都好，文宣又好同朋友宣傳又好出去做佈景版又好，希望大家互相尊重，努力做好自己個部份，守住香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46968fec58e0f1d12dc753eaf732daa9d52519c","tid":497650,"uid":336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b45c9f55911b881671c607e7d454ea7c3867877","tid":497650,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edcb559f9fd78d2e5d7e56346687dd8d7ced4cd5","tid":497650,"uid":25494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"呼之則來揮之則去<br />\n有事就大團結出事就屌鳩你<br />\nCall人話聲援抗爭者原來只幫13+3籌款<br />\n都係不了"},{"pid":"39fe8b69eab25171a22ddb9e279d8d85e6b26b80","tid":497650,"uid":48276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"呢D對白睇左十幾年<br />\n改下keyword又可以用得<br />\n有邊次唔係危急關頭啊"},{"pid":"cedebcfd3a48490b5d1124cad04119a00a1ac7c6","tid":497650,"uid":138689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"437bf5758602574322928686ca141cc047a1aa20","tid":497650,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4175092fb442d0bfee19709e561cdaf5493f6c4","tid":497650,"uid":25494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"泛民咁多人撐，泛民支持者去左邊？<br />\n要人抗爭個陣就要班少數派本土撚出來撐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12804a4a65f8dd440740797928aa728e20e01497","tid":497650,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/124512_5bf7c943687ed8bb5b3fef4f900ffec0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F124512_5bf7c943687ed8bb5b3fef4f900ffec0.jpg&h=20010596&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c2f17fb5385b540d2e7f652c50b0655360d88f9","tid":497650,"uid":336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呼之則來揮之則去<br />\n有事就大團結出事就屌鳩你<br />\nCall人話聲援抗爭者原來只幫13+3籌款<br />\n都係不了</blockquote><br />\n咁咪自己本土搞一個囉，泛民個邊無人嚟自然會收皮啦。<br />\n你想本土成事都要做啲事主導返個運動架啦，係屋企講有咩用。<br />\n同埋依家學聯已經有無分界別嘅抗爭者基金，魚革嘅人都可以申請架。<br />\n佢唔受你，你咪自己搞大佢，令到佢無得唔聽本土嘅聲音，而唔係好似依家咁將抗爭成本高同埋唔想去歸咎去兩派之爭，咁樣互屌有意思咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06510d7975c0e32679068a8b521c4444f116f982","tid":497650,"uid":336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泛民咁多人撐，泛民支持者去左邊？<br />\n要人抗爭個陣就要班少數派本土撚出來撐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係個句，你自己搞個本土集會，係撐本土撐自己，以本土定位反對議事規則，無衝突架啵，依家淨係得泛民個個你揀，咪自己創造一個新嘅option出嚟囉，唔洗幫泛民站台，幫嘅係自己。"},{"pid":"20e937deb9cecb70b33dceff96592baeefb6eec2","tid":497650,"uid":336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54a79c2b0057c1c98f3996f2c98ba35beddf540b","tid":497650,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"跟住畀人力篤灰 民主黨譴責 本民青出賣？咪on9啦 香港死左啦"}]}